Indonesian rupiah plunges on speculative attack . The Indonesian rupiah plunged against the dollar in nervous trading on Monday , with offshore players seen sustaining a speculative attack , dealers said . " We have become the main target today . Offshore players seem to switch focus to the rupiah after they had launched attacks last week on the ringgit and the Singapore dollar , " one dealer in Singapore said . Spot rupiah was quoted at 2 , 620 / 30 at 0250 GMT , compared with an opening at 2 , 510 / 20 . 
